<div class="main-tab-content">
  <div class="tab-col-left">
    <h2>In the Moment</h2>
    <p>I ran a technical analysis blog for about a year. I used a simple blog engine to manage a service that delivered plays to futures and commodities traders. At its peak, 300 reoccurring visitors had been leveraging my free information.<br><br>It grew really intense for a moment. I was using the Google chat widget to communicate with traders while they were trading. At any given moment, I was pumping out advice and screenshots to 6 or 7 traders simultaneously while dozens of others were constantly commenting on the site.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-col-mid">
    <div class="tab-bullets">
      <p class="title">Goals</p>
      <ul>
        <li><span>Chart the market and provide screenshots of particular plays</span></li>
        <li><span>Create a place to learn how to chart a particular market</span></li>
        <li><span>Build enough following to eventually monetize</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="title">Overview</p>
      <p>Using the CQG, I would create 1, 5, 15, hourly and daily screenshots of trends and give guidance on how to play things like triangles, head and shoulder patterns, etc.</p>
      <div class="home-slideshow slideshow-nine">
        <div><%= image_tag "layout/marketing_portal/slide_trendlevel_1.jpg", :alt => "" %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
      <div id="home_slide_nav9" class="home_slide_nav"></div>
      <div class="clear"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-col-right"></div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>

<%= javascript_tag do -%>
$(document).ready(function(){
  
  $().framerate({framerate: 30})
  var rand = $('.slideshow-nine > div').length;
  $('.slideshow-nine').cycle({
    pager: '#home_slide_nav9',
    cleartype: 1,
    timeout:0,
    startingSlide: Math.floor(Math.random() * rand),
    fx: 'none'
  });
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").css({opacity: 0, visibility: "visible"});
  var html = $(".hidden-media-widget").html();
  $(".hidden-media-widget").remove();
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").html(html);
  $("#connect_and_exchange_wrapper").css({opacity: 0, visibility: "visible"}).animate({opacity: 1}, 1000);
  
  $(".mast-text").hide();
  $(".mast-text").slideDown("slow");
});

<% end -%>

